<div id="review_3853819357" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3853819357" />
    <a title="Lata" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/13126933-lata"><img alt="Lata" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1525485137p2/13126933.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3853819357?book_show_action=true">Feb 23, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lata" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lata" href="/user/show/13126933-lata">Lata</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="ebook 9780807006245" href="/book/show/13641983-notes-of-a-native-son">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13126933-lata?shelf=classic">classic</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13126933-lata?shelf=2021-read">2021-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13126933-lata?shelf=bipoc-author">bipoc-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/13126933-lata?shelf=bipoc-actor">bipoc-actor</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3853819357" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14237697429760969351">Each of the short essays in this collection made incisive comments on American culture and its relationship with race. I wanted to highlight particularly trenchant statements (or paragraphs) but realized that much of this book would be marked up. So much of what Baldwin said in these essays is depressingly still current, in many cases.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


